Original: As you touch the plain door, you hear

closed.

Original: At the end of the path, you find

[Page]
Most of the pages are now unreadable,
but you can make out the following...
[Page]
"Yggdrasil Sealing Project, Summary 2
Each seal requires a corresponding
tablet arranged by a protector.
[Page]
"But due to the loss of... we lack
sufficient protectors. We must place
the tablets on the outer ring and..."
[Page]
More than that is impossible to read.
You leave the book behind and hurry
on ahead.

memory or ignore it altogether.
